<plot>Flying economy class, the Pink Panther is parachuted into the Arctic, where he befriends a lonely seal pup. The young seal doesn't want the Pink Panther to leave him and cries tears that freeze into ice cubes. So, the compassionate Pink Panther stays, to find that he must defend the seal from a trapper. The ensuing conflict awakens and angers a hibernating polar bear!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433343</url></doc>
